ygData.subject: Re: Warrens on Tues. July 3rd
ygData.msgSnippet: Too bad we did not have enough, the zone has a lot to offer our lvls I think. With a full group we could of gone deeper. My Paly could use cold iron armor
ygData.messageBody:
Too bad we did not have enough, the zone has a
lot to offer our lvls I think. With a full group we
could of gone deeper. My Paly could use cold iron armor
pieces to replace the heavy bronze. Also he's in need of
some cool paly weapons so maybe big brother Jonquil
will have to do some shoppin for him (poor Jonquil has
to support all his little brothers). I am definetly
up for trying it again, I'll let my guild know ahead
of time as well so we could possibly get a group or
two there.
